README

Introduction

This is an attempt at writing an IP-radio application based on Cappuccino(http://cappuccino.org/) and the SoundManager API (http://schillmania.com/projects/sundmanager2/). The Download containes the front end to test this app.

The images, songs and SoundManager.js code can be found on the resurces directory.

Getting help

If you need help with XYZRadio, you can get help from the following sources:

	-FAQ 
	-Wiki: http://github.com/Alos/xyzradio/wikis

If you discover any bugs, please file a ticket on github.

